Harry Kane was captain for Tottenham Hotspur in the Premier League match against Burnley at Turf Moor . 
  Kane was the youngest Premier League captain this season at the age of 21 years and 251 days . 
  Burnley striker Danny Ings scored the only goal of the game in the first half . 
  Mauricio Pochettino's side are still in the Champions League hunt . 
 